<SLUG> BC-`GOLDILOCKS'-ECONOMY-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GOLDILOCKS OR GRIDLOCK?: U.S. ECONOMY IS TOO HOT  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This excellent 700-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
