<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-21 13:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3758 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MOVIES-HUSBAND-BOS &LR;      06-21 1287
