<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-21 13:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3770 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-PEOPLE-BOS &LR;      06-21 1118
