   COMING DVD ATTRACTIONS: June 15: ``Enemy of the State,''
``Dancing at Lughnasa,'' ``The Faculty,'' ``Nixon,'' ``White
Squall,'' ``Arachnophobia,'' ``Mrs. Brown,'' ``Brassed Off,''
``Flirting With Disaster.'' June 22: ``Barbarella,'' ``Billy
Jack,'' ``Jawbreaker,'' ``The Old Dark House,'' ``The Parallax
View,'' ``Patch Adams _ Collector's Edition,'' ``A Simple Plan,''
``Suicide Kings,'' ``Tender Mercies.'' June 29: ``Barry Lyndon,''
