</P>
<P>
   NETWATCHER _ The dating game on the Web. (Katz, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   CYBERSCENE _ While there is enough practical information to suit
the most dour Web surfer, there also are plenty of light features
that are just plain fun. We'll start with horoscopes. (Husted,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   TECH-MEDIA _ The inside scoop on the latest version of Microsoft
