<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    JUDGE: MICROSOFT'S INTENT HOLDS KEY TO VERDICT
 &HT;    Eds: Corrects ``Microsoft's'' to ``Microsoft `` in lede.
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
