activism among state attorneys general, Republicans are creating
their party's own attorneys general association to promote an idea
of more limited government and raise money for the election of more
Republicans to positions as the states' chief law enforcement
officers. By Alison Mitchell. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in
``w'' news file.)
</P>
