<P>
   (NYT1) UNDATED -- June 21, 1999 --SCI-INFECTION-THE-GAME, 6-21
-- Infection, a new board game which is sort of a cross between
Monopoly and Trivial Pursuit, pits from two to nine people against
one another on a playing field run rampant with disease. The first
player who is completely cured or, in a less hopeful scenario, is
the only one left alive -- wins. (Tony Cenicolla/New York Times
Photo) LITE
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
