Martin Greenblatt's snoring escalated from a hum to a rasping buzz.
This is a fairly common later-in-life male development, but one
that can seriously affect spousal relations. ``When your partner
can't sleep because you're sawing wood, she can build up a pretty
good head of resentment,'' says Martin, 59, a Boston lawyer. (Janet
Knott/Boston Globe Photo)
