brought his wiry energy to ``The Breakfast Club'' and ``Sixteen
Candles,'' Anthony Michael Hall has returned to the spotlight,
playing the Harvard-era Bill Gates in TNT's ``Pirates of Silicon
Valley.'' (Boston Globe Photo)
